ume a baseline prefix of `/api`. All JSON schemas represent strict Pydantic structures.\n+82: \n+83: ---\n+84: \n+85: ### 4.1. POST /api/blueprint/generate\n+86: \n+87: **Purpose**: Persistently stores and generates an advanced strategic enterprise AI architecture blueprint based on target constraints, compliance frameworks, and infrastructure choices.\n+88: \n+89: *   **HTTP Method**: `POST`\n+90: *   **Path**: `/api/blueprint/generate`\n+91: *   **Security Requirement**: Optional Session Authentication (registers draft anonymously or links to authenticated user profile).\n+92: *   **Request Payload Schema (JSON)**:\n+93:     ```json\n+94:     {\n+95:       \"company_name\": \"Acme Global Enterprise\",\n+96:       \"industry\": \"Financial Services\",\n+97:       \"compliance_frameworks\": [\"SOC2\", \"HIPAA\", \"EU_AI_ACT\"],\n+98:       \"data_residency\": \"EU_WEST\",\n+99:       \"infrastructure_preference\": \"Sovereign_Cloud\",\n+100:       \"deployment_scale\": \"Enterprise_Wide\",\n+101:       \"selected_capabilities\": [\n+102:         \"Knowledge_Graph_Mesh\",\n+103:         \"Autonomous_Agent_Orchestrators\",\n+104:         \"Governance_Guardrails\"\n+105:       ],\n+106:       \"budget_tier\": \"Premium_Enterprise\"\n+107:     }\n+108:     ```\n+109: *   **Response Payload (`[ILLUSTRATIVE MOCK]`)**:\n+110:     ```json\n+111:     {\n+112:       \"blueprint_id\": \"blu_908f7e21-3a0c-4991-88b1-38f7e1b99c72\",\n+113:       \"created_at\": \"2026-06-27T10:30:15Z\",\n+114:       \"compliance_rating\": 98.4,\n+115:       \"estimated_deployment_time_weeks\": 12,\n+116:       \"recommended_architecture_nodes\": [\n+117:         {\n+118:           \"id\": \"node-1\",\n+119:           \"label\": \"GFF AI Sovereign Edge\",\n+120:           \"type\": \"infrastructure\",\n+121:           \"status\": \"critical\"\n+122:         },\n+123:         {\n+124:           \"id\": \"node-2\",\n+125:           \"label\": \"Agent Orchestration Mesh\",\n+126:           \"type\": \"orchestrator\",\n+127:           \"status\": \"active\"\n+128:         }\n+129:       ],\n+130:       \"generated_narrative\": \"Based on financial service constraints, GFF AI prescribes a secure, sovereign-hosted multi-agent cluster backed by real-time governance guardrails.\",\n+131:       \"pdf_download_url\": \"https://assets.gff.ai/blueprints/blu_908f7e21_export.pdf\"\n+132:     }\n+133:     ```\n+134: *   **Error Responses**:\n+135:     *   `400 Bad Request`: If empty inputs or incompatibilities exist in selected frameworks.\n+136:     *   `422 Unprocessable Entity`: Validation failure on Pydantic models (e.g. invalid string enum in `data_residency`).\n+137: \n```","success":true},"durationMs":2}}
